      <h3>The Greatest Football Tournament</h3>
        <p>The FIFA World Cup is a showcase of the greatest footballing nations on the planet. Every four years a tournament featuring 32 teams from around the world compete for the trophy.</p>
        <p>The 2018 edition will be hosted in Russia and matches will be played in twelve different stadiums around the country. Learn about the stadiums, Russia's preperations to host the torunament, and other important information regarding the tournament below.</p>
